# Data Folder README

## Introduction
This directory contains preprocessed data files in CSV format used for the song genre classification project.

## Data Files Description
- `train.csv`: Used for training the model, contains columns for 'lyrics', 'genre', 'artist', and 'language'. This dataset is further split 85-15 into train dataset and validation dataset.
- `test.csv`: Test dataset for evaluating the model's performance.

## How to Use the Data
- Use `train.csv` for training the model with the respective lyrics and genre labels.
- Use `test.csv` to test the model's performance after training.

## Citation/Source
The original dataset is from Kaggle dataset: Multilingual Lyrics for Genre Classification (https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mateibejan/multilingual-lyrics-for-genre-classification)
